name: fog and electricity
description:
On February 2, 2021, there was a heavy fog in our city. I was lucky enough to capture this natural phenomenon with my camera. Electricity and fog are two magical ingredients that give my work a mystical atmosphere. The first simultaneously illuminates and destroys some things, while the second gives a halo of mystery to the phenomenon.

Location: Kharkiv, Ukraine
Date of photo creation: February 2, 2021
JPEG is 6000x4000 pixels
